    "One may wonder, however, whether this analysis depends on the choice of consent-based views of legitimacy.",
    "Would a different approach to legitimacy lead to alternative requirements of transparency?",
    "While one doesn't get to all three requirements in most cases, I think that these three provide a happy medium between alternative accounts that pick up on the central points of all of them.",
